special_powers.name: BREATH OF LIFE
special_powers.description: STOP. FREE: Once per game, roll a d6 and add the number of Soul tokens to the result. 6 or higher: Replace this character with a character named Thor of a lower point value on its last non-KO click, then heal that character equal to the number of Soul tokens.

special_powers.name: ON THE RUN
special_powers.description: Stealth. Sidestep, but only if an opposing character is within 4 squares.

special_powers.name: OLD LACE MUST BE AROUND HERE SOMEWHERE
special_powers.description: Blades/Claws/Fangs, but only if an old Lace Bystander has not been generated this game. // POWER: Once per game, generate an Old Lace bystader adjacent or in a square of hindering terrain within 4 squares.

special_powers.name: TIME TO GO, GANG
special_powers.description: Leadership. Friendly characters with the Runaways keyword can use Improved Movement: Characters.

special_powers.name: NO TIME FOR SUBTLETY
special_powers.description: Super Senses. Black Panther has PROTECTED: Pulse Wave. If Black Panther is 150 points, he is KO'd when he cross the red KO line.

special_powers.name: WIELDING THE GAUNTLET
special_powers.description: FREE: If Black Panther is on click #1-6, turn Black Panther's dial to another click from #1 to #6, noting his current click. If you do, at the end of your turn, return him to the noted click.

special_powers.name: FEROCITY OF A WARRIOR KING
special_powers.description: Charge, Flurry.

special_powers.name: RELEASE THE DEAD TO TURN THE TIDE
special_powers.description: STOP. Combat Reflexes, Toughness. When this click is first revealed, after resolutions generate two Zombie Warrior bystanders. Black Panther can't be healed.

special_powers.name: ONE WHO TRAVELS A SIEGE COURAGEOUS IS GRANTED A NEW LIFE
special_powers.description: Phasing/Teleport, Passenger: 4. When Namor uses Phasing/Teleport to move in a direct path of at least 4 squares, after resolutions heal Namor and one character he carried 1 click.

special_powers.name: THE SCION OF ATLANTIS REFUSES TO FALL
special_powers.description: Combat Reflexes, Regeneration, Toughness.

special_powers.name: A KING DOES NOT BARGAIN, HE COMMANDS!
special_powers.description: Leadership. When Namor uses it and succeeds, after resolutions you may give one of his action tokens to an adjacent character with 0 or 1 action tokens (friendly or opposing).

special_powers.name: BARON OF BATTLEWORLD
special_powers.description: Leadership, Perplex. When Sheriff Strange uses Perplex to target another character, you may instead modify a combat value except damage +2 if the target shares a Battleworld keyword or -2 if it has a different Battleworld keyword.

special_powers.name: THE WALLS OF BATTLEWORLD MUST REMAIN INVIOLATE
special_powers.description: Opposing characters must use a DOUBLE POWER action instead of POWER action to activate ID cards.

special_powers.name: THERE IS ONLY ONE WILL THAT RULES HERE
special_powers.description: Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When Sheriff Strange uses it, after resolutions hit characters can't use or become equipped by Equipment until your next turn. (Includes Equipment-Characters.)

special_powers.name: SCATTERED TO THE WINS
special_powers.description: STOP. When this click is first revealed, if you paid 100 points for Sheriff Strange, after resolutions you may place all other friendly characters within range into squares within 3 squares of the square they currently occupy.

special_powers.name: SCATTERED TO THE WINDS
special_powers.description: STOP. When this click is first revealed, if you paid 100 points for Sheriff Strange, after resolutions you may place all other friendly characters within range into squares within 3 squares of the square they currently occupy.

special_powers.name: BEFORE MARTIAL ARTS
special_powers.description: Adjacent opposing characters can't use Flurry, Precision Strike, Combat Reflexes, or Close Combat Expert.

special_powers.name: ANCIENT INCARNATION: IRON FIST
special_powers.description: When another friendly character named Iron Fist hits, after resolutions remove an action token from this character.

special_powers.name: THE FIRST IRON FIST
special_powers.description: Charge, Flurry. If Iron Fist is adjacent to an opposing character, she can't become the target of range attacks.

special_powers.name: THE ALL-SEEING
special_powers.description: When Agamotto uses Perplex or Probability Control, he may target opposing characters regardless of range or line of fire unless that character is the lowest-point character on its force.

special_powers.name: BEFORE MYSTICAL ARTS
special_powers.description: PROTECTED: Mystics team ability. Opposing characters within 3 square can't use Perplex or Probability Control.

special_powers.name: ANCIENT INCARNATION: DR. STRANGE
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Dr. Strange hits, after resolutions remove an action token from this character.

special_powers.name: BEFORE IMMORTALS WERE COMMON
special_powers.description: Adjacent opposing characters can't be healed, can't use PROTECTED: Outwit, and can't use STOP clicks.

special_powers.name: STOP TRYING TO ESCAPE ME, MJOLNIR!
special_powers.description: FREE: Once per game, make a range attack with a range value of 8.

special_powers.name: ANCIENT INCARNATION: THOR
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Thor hits, after resolutions remove an action token from this character.

special_powers.name: BRAINS AND BRAWN
special_powers.description: Perplex, but only to target herself or another character she shares a keyword with.

special_powers.name: BOWLING PINS!
special_powers.description: Quake.  When She-Hulk uses Quake, the number of squares characters would be knocked back is doubled.
